original_title: Girl Internet Show: A Kati Kelli Mixtape
overview: This feature-length “mixtape” curated by Jane Schoenbrun and Jordan Wippell reintroduces a stunning body of work by Kati Kelli, an outsider YouTube artist who ran “Girl Internet Show” before her passing in 2019.
title: Girl Internet Show: A Kati Kelli Mixtape
